				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<h3 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default"><a href="https://megawineandspirits.com/loch-lomond-vintage-2002-cristie-kerr-ed-750ml/">LOCH LOMOND Vintage 2002 Cristie Kerr Ed 750ml</a></h3>				</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-e61ef64 elementor-widget elementor-widget-theme-post-content" data-id="e61ef64" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="theme-post-content.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<p data-path-to-node="3"><b data-path-to-node="3" data-index-in-node="0">Loch Lomond Vintage 2002 Cristie Kerr Edition</b> is an exceptional Single Malt Scotch Whisky, crafted by Master Distiller Michael Henry in collaboration with LPGA champion and Hall of Famer, Cristie Kerr. This limited edition captures the shared excellence and precision of professional golf and artisanal distilling, offering a complex flavor profile matured to perfection over two decades.</p>
<p data-path-to-node="4,0,0"><b data-path-to-node="4,0,0" data-index-in-node="0">Brand:</b> Loch Lomond (Limited Edition Cristie Kerr)<br /><b data-path-to-node="4,1,0" data-index-in-node="0">Type of Drink:</b> Single Malt Scotch Whisky<br /><b data-path-to-node="4,2,0" data-index-in-node="0">Origin:</b> Highlands, Scotland<br /><b data-path-to-node="4,3,0" data-index-in-node="0">Special Feature:</b> Distilled in 2002 and aged in hand-selected American oak casks, finished in California red wine casks (sourced from Cristie Kerr’s own winery). It features deep notes of honey, forest fruits, vanilla, and a subtle touch of toasted spices.<br /><b data-path-to-node="4,4,0" data-index-in-node="0">Alcohol Grade:</b> Typically 48.1% ABV.<br /><b data-path-to-node="4,5,0" data-index-in-node="0">Content:</b> 750 ml<br /><b data-path-to-node="5,0" data-index-in-node="0">Disclaimer:</b> Please consume alcohol responsibly. Excessive alcohol consumption can lead to health problems. You must be of legal drinking age to purchase and consume alcoholic beverages in your country. Do not consume if pregnant or suspecting pregnancy. Check packaging for accurate ingredient list information.</p>
				</div>
				</div>
