				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<p>Kim Crawford Prosecco 750ml is an Italian sparkling wine that stands out for its freshness and vivacity. Made with Glera grapes from the Veneto region, this Prosecco offers fruity and floral aromas and flavors, with notes of pear, citrus, and almond. Its fine and elegant effervescence makes it an ideal choice for celebrations or to enjoy as an aperitif. <br /><strong>Brand:</strong> Kim Crawford <br /><strong>Type drink:</strong> Prosecco (Sparkling Wine) <br /><strong>Origin:</strong> Italy, Veneto. <br /><strong>Special Feature:</strong> Made with Glera grapes, produced using the Charmat method. <br /><strong>Alcohol Grade:</strong> Approximately 11%. <br /><strong>Content:</strong> 750 ml <br /><strong>Year of Manufacture:</strong> N/A (Non Vintage) <br /><strong> Ingredients:</strong> Glera grapes. Check packaging for accurate Ingredient list information. <br /><strong>Disclaimer:</strong> Please consume alcohol responsibly. Excessive alcohol consumption can lead to health problems. You must be 21 years of age or older to purchase and consume alcoholic beverages in the United States. Do not consume if pregnant or suspecting pregnancy.</p>
