					<h3 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default"><a href="https://megawineandspirits.com/whispering-angel-rose-750-ml/">WHISPERING ANGEL Rose 750 ml</a></h3>				</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-e61ef64 elementor-widget elementor-widget-theme-post-content" data-id="e61ef64" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="theme-post-content.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<p>Whispering Angel Rosé 750 ml is a large format bottle (Magnum) of the world-renowned rosé wine from Provence, France. Made primarily with Grenache, Cinsault, and Rolle (Vermentino) grapes, this wine stands out for its attractive pale pink color and its rewarding flavor profile. It is a dry wine with a full and smooth texture on the palate, offering aromas of fresh red berries and floral notes. It is considered a benchmark in Provence rosés, appreciated for its elegance, freshness, and gastronomic versatility, ideal for pairing from appetizers to light dishes such as salads, seafood, and lemon chicken. </p>
<p><strong>Brand:</strong> Château d&#8217;Esclans (Whispering Angel is one of their lines) <br /><strong>Origin:</strong> France (Provence) <br /><strong>Quantity: </strong>750 ml (Magnum). <br /><strong>Disclaimer :</strong> Please consume alcohol responsibly. Excessive alcohol consumption can lead to health problems. You must be 21 years of age or older to purchase and consume alcoholic beverages in the United States. Do not consume if pregnant or suspecting pregnancy.</p>
