				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-0bbe2c4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-theme-post-title elementor-page-title elementor-widget-heading" data-id="0bbe2c4" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="theme-post-title.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<h3 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default"><a href="https://megawineandspirits.com/jameson-black-barrel-select-reserve-750-ml/">JAMESON Black Barrel Select Reserve 750 ml</a></h3>				</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-e61ef64 elementor-widget elementor-widget-theme-post-content" data-id="e61ef64" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="theme-post-content.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<p>Jameson Black Barrel is a distinctive Irish whiskey that builds upon the smooth character of Jameson Original with an intensified flavor profile. It&#8217;s a blended whiskey, meaning it combines different types of whiskey to achieve its unique taste. The key feature of Black Barrel is its maturation process: it&#8217;s aged in double-charred barrels, which involves an additional charring of the bourbon barrels. This process is intended to bring out more vanilla, caramel, and toasted wood notes, resulting in a richer, more complex whiskey with a smooth finish.   Brand: Jameson Type of Drink: Irish Whiskey (Blended)   Origin: Ireland Special Features: Triple distilled, matured in a combination of sherry casks and double-charred bourbon barrels, non-chill filtered in some cases, often described as having enhanced vanilla and caramel notes due to the double-charring.   Alcohol Grade: Typically 40% ABV (Alcohol By Volume) / 80 Proof. Content: 750 ml Disclaimer: Please consume alcohol responsibly. Excessive alcohol consumption can lead to health problems. You must be 21 years of age or older to purchase and consume alcoholic beverages in the United States. Do not consume if pregnant or suspecting pregnancy.</p>
				</div>
				</div>
