				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<p>Elijah Craig Small Batch is a highly regarded Kentucky bourbon, known for its rich and complex flavor. This bourbon is made with a blend of corn, rye, and malted barley grains, and aged in charred oak barrels. The result is a bourbon with notes of caramel, vanilla, spice, and oak. the 1.75L version is ideal for gatherings, or celebrations. Brand: Elijah Craig. Drink Type: Bourbon Whiskey. Origin: United States (Kentucky). Special Features: Small Batch, aged in charred oak barrels. Alcohol Grade: 47% ABV (94 proof). Content: 1.75 L. Ingredients: Corn, rye, malted barley, water. (Check packaging for accurate ingredient list). Disclaimer: Please consume alcohol responsibly. Excessive alcohol consumption can lead to health problems. You must be 21 years of age or older to purchase and consume alcoholic beverages in the United States. Do not consume if pregnant or suspecting pregnancy.</p>
				</div>
