				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<h3 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default"><a href="https://megawineandspirits.com/appleton-estate-8-year-reserve-750-ml/">APPLETON ESTATE 8 Year Reserve 750 ml</a></h3>				</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-e61ef64 elementor-widget elementor-widget-theme-post-content" data-id="e61ef64" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="theme-post-content.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<p>The Appleton Estate 8 Year Old Reserve is a Jamaican rum that celebrates the richness and complexity of aged rums. It is a blend of rums that have matured for a minimum of 8 years in oak barrels, giving it a distinctive flavor profile. This rum is characterized by its notes of spiced fruits, honey, vanilla, and a hint of orange peel, characteristic of the brand.<br />
It is a versatile rum, ideal for enjoying alone, on the rocks or in cocktails.</p>
<p><strong>Brand:</strong> Appleton Estate.<br />
<strong>Drink type:</strong>  Aged Rum.<br />
<strong>Origin:</strong>  Jamaica.<br />
<strong>Special features:</strong> Aged for a minimum of 8 years in oak barrels. Blend of select rums. Flavor profile with notes of spiced fruits, honey, vanilla and orange peel. Versatile for cocktails.<br />
<strong>Alcohol Grade:</strong>  Approximately 43% (may vary slightly).<br />
<strong>Content:</strong>  750 ml.<br />
<strong>Ingredients:</strong>  Sugar cane molasses, water, yeast, and the compounds obtained during maturation in oak barrels. Check packaging for accurate Ingredient list information.<br />
<strong>Disclaimer:</strong>  Please consume alcohol responsibly. Excessive alcohol consumption can lead to health problems. You must be 21 years of age or older to purchase and consume alcoholic beverages in the United States. Do not consume if pregnant or suspecting pregnancy.</p>
				</div>
