				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<p>Flor de Caña 7 Year Gran Reserva is a premium rum aged for a minimum of seven years in small oak barrels. It&#8217;s known for its smooth and complex flavor profile with notes of vanilla, caramel, spice, and dried fruit. <strong>Brand:</strong>  FLOR DE CANA <strong>Type of drink:</strong>   Aged rum <strong>Item From:</strong> Glass bottle <strong>Origin:</strong> Nicaragua <strong>Special Features:</strong> Sustainable production <strong>Alcohol grade:</strong> 40% ABV <strong>Content:</strong> 750 ml <strong>Year of manufacture:</strong> 7 years <strong>Ingredients:</strong> Sugarcane distillate. Check packaging for accurate Ingredient list information. <strong>Consume indications:</strong> Enjoy it neat or on the rocks to savor the complex flavors and smooth finish. It can be used in a variety of cocktails, adding depth and complexity. Try it in a Daiquiri, Old Fashioned, or Mojito. <strong>Disclaimer:</strong> Please consume alcohol responsibly. Excessive alcohol consumption can lead to health problems. You must be 21 years of age or older to purchase and consume alcoholic beverages in the United States. Please do not consume if pregnant or suspecting pregnancy.</p>
