					<p>Woodford Reserve Wheated is a special addition to the Woodford Reserve Master&#8217;s Collection lineup. This Kentucky Straight Bourbon Whiskey is distinguished by its &#8220;wheated&#8221; grain recipe, where soft wheat replaces the rye traditionally used in most bourbons. This grain selection imparts a smoother, sweeter, and more approachable flavor profile. It presents aromas of honey, orchard fruits (like pear and apple), creamy vanilla, soft caramel, and a hint of sweet spices. On the palate, it offers a silky texture with flavors of caramel, toffee, ripe fruits, a light citrus touch, and subtle oak notes. The finish is long, smooth, and sweet, with a pleasant warmth. Woodford Reserve Wheated is appreciated for its balance and inherent sweetness, making it ideal for sipping neat or in cocktails where a softer bourbon base is desired. <strong>Brand:</strong>: Woodford Reserve <strong>Origin:</strong>: United States, specifically Kentucky. <strong>Quantity:</strong>: 750 ml. <strong>Disclaimer :</strong> Please consume alcohol responsibly. Excessive alcohol consumption can lead tohealth problems. You must be 21 years of age or older to purchase and consume alcoholicbeverages in the United States. Do not consume if pregnant or suspecting pregnancy.</p>
				</div>
				</div>
