				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<h3 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default"><a href="https://megawineandspirits.com/johnnie-walker-black-50-ml/">JOHNNIE WALKER Black 50 ml</a></h3>				</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-e61ef64 elementor-widget elementor-widget-theme-post-content" data-id="e61ef64" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="theme-post-content.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<p>Johnnie Walker Black Label 50 ml is a miniature version of the renowned 12-year-old blended Scotch whisky. It retains the same complex and smooth blend of over 40 malt and grain whiskies from across Scotland, offering distinctive notes of dark fruits, vanilla, and a smoky touch. Its compact size makes it ideal for sampling, for travel, or as a small gift. <strong>Brand:</strong> Johnnie Walker <strong>Origin:</strong> Scotland, United Kingdom <strong>Special Feature:</strong>: Blend of over 40 malt and grain whiskies, each aged for at least 12 years. 50 ml presentation. <strong>Alcohol Grade:</strong> 40% <strong>Content:</strong> 50 ml <strong>Ingredients:</strong> Grains, malt, water, caramel (for color). Check packaging for accurate Ingredient list information. <strong>Disclaimer:</strong> Please consume alcohol responsibly. Excessive alcohol consumption can lead to health problems. You must be 21 years of age or older to purchase and consume alcoholic beverages in the United States. Do not consume if pregnant or suspecting pregnancy.</p>
				</div>
