				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<h3 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default"><a href="https://megawineandspirits.com/chivas-regal-15yr-50-ml/">CHIVAS REGAL 15Yr 50 ml</a></h3>				</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-e61ef64 elementor-widget elementor-widget-theme-post-content" data-id="e61ef64" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="theme-post-content.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<p>Chivas Regal 15 Year Old is a premium blended Scotch whisky. It is characterized by its rich and fruity flavor, with notes of baked apple, honey, cinnamon, and a hint of vanilla. Its 15-year maturation in select oak casks gives it exceptional smoothness and complexity. <strong>Brand:</strong> Chivas Regal <strong><strong>Type drink:</strong></strong> Blended Scotch Whisky <strong>Origin:</strong> Scotland <strong>Special Feature:</strong> Matured for 15 years, part of Chivas Regal&#8217;s range of premium blended whiskies. <strong>Alcohol Grade:</strong> 40% ABV <strong>Content:</strong> 50 ml (Also available in standard sizes such as 700 ml or 750 ml) <strong>Year of manufacture:</strong> 15 years. <strong>Ingredients:</strong> Water, malted barley, other grains. Check packaging for accurate Ingredient list information. <strong>Disclaimer:</strong> Please consume alcohol responsibly. Excessive alcohol consumption can lead to health problems. You must be 21 years of age or older to purchase and consume alcoholic beverages in the United States. Do not consume if pregnant or suspecting pregnancy.</p>
				</div>
				</div>
